@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam arrowColor #1d3557
skinparam rectangleFontColor #1d3557
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #1d3557
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #f1faee
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #fdf6e3
skinparam noteBorderColor #b07f00

start
:Specify security stories\nThreat model & classification; 
Use VP+PlantUML exports;[green]

:Test design\nAbuse-case tests\nFail-first security checks;[gold]

:Design solution\nSelect patterns (e.g., signed token)\nTraceability to DSM/Secure Tropos;[lightblue]

:Develop code\nSecure coding checklist\nLinters & secret scanning;[lightpink]

:Verify\nPytest + security tests\nDependency/dynamic scans;[palegreen]

:Deploy\nSigned artifacts + IaC policy checks;[beige]

:Monitor & learn\nSecurity observability, rate-limit alerts\nFeed incidents back to Specify;[wheat]

:Close loop\nRefine models in VP + PlantUML;[lightgray]

stop
@enduml
